{
  "texts": [
    "We also considered using fake facts for introducing new knowledge, but we were concerned that this would introduce confounding factors into our study, as fake facts may behave differently than real ones.",
    "We discuss this in detail in §F.",
    "In our study we achieve this by using exemplars from the same relation.",
    "E.g., if q =\"Where is Paris located?",
    "\", the exemplars would follow the pattern \"Where is {X} located?"
  ]
}